    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-14">14 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>Press release</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/millions-invested-to-help-people-get-active-in-their-communities">Millions invested to help people get active in their communities</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>£3 million to be spent in 16 boroughs, towns and cities across England to encourage more people to get involved in local issues</p>
</div></div>


